data.description: Step into this beautiful, larger floor-plan that is welcoming to families, first time home buyers and those who just need some extra living room. Home to some of the best school districts make the location even more appealing. Entering into the home you have a “flex” room that can be used as a dining room, office, study or gym. There is a huge great room that opens to the kitchen allowing for large gatherings. The kitchen is spacious with counter space, cabinets and pantry. The laundry room is situated upstairs near the bedrooms for extra convenience. The large master suite contains a walk-in closet, double vanity sinks, and shower. There are updated fixtures throughout. Privacy fence is already installed and a storage shed that provides extra storage space. Neighborhood is quiet, walkable with sidewalks.  Home also comes equipped with Solar Panel system. Instant savings on energy costs!  All information listed to be verified by buyer(s) and/or agent.
